{"tid":1625732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家唔好再搞特許經營嘅舖頭","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T09:50:41.000Z","uid":199718,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8a661d39d9aefad5ff565e751b837a786e6b2d84","tid":1625732,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:06:45.000Z","msg":"因為唔肯定老闆係藍係黃，為免搞錯同路人，建議停止裝修<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特許經營</span></span>嘅舖頭。<br />\n<br />\n小弟見識淺薄，希望各位列多啲特許經營嘅舖頭比大家知道。<br />\n<br />\n一芳係個例子。"},{"pid":"13d4491106b834deddc5b42d461f89f92d95c465","tid":1625732,"uid":259993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:08:14.000Z","msg":"推 其實中資加福建幫 美西 已經好夠"},{"pid":"8df7b91e55968e658ed6412d4cfe06b2a047daf8","tid":1625732,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f024e8ecbb9e043a6a2fff8036d9379a0c42ce23","tid":1625732,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:09:11.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。"},{"pid":"25b9e0248f117d8c33e78e51d494c9f04812884f","tid":1625732,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"eec3e71fb602d8bdddefbf7281be1a4b8e06535a","tid":1625732,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:10:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3fbaa69dec0ca68e9a57a175b655bde75e8d625f","tid":1625732,"uid":199718,"like":0,"di